<div class="nbunit" id="27Aug1937"><font color="red">27 August 1937</font> <i>NLPL</i> (to Paul L&eacute;on): Brentano&apos;s. Please phone. If they have not delivered or reported on book ordered from London 3 weeks ago cancel order and transfer to Gal. et Cie. <i>Food and Character</i> by Dr Louis Berman. Methuen. London. </div>
